                <h1>Mayor reflects on Durham growth after State of the City speech</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/7fcedece-c22e-4905-9fc0-6cdae5a8539d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Durham&#x20;Mayor&#x20;Bill&#x20;Bell&#x20;is&#x20;focused&#x20;on&#x20;improving&#x20;transportation&#x20;and&#x20;reducing&#x20;poverty&#x20;as&#x20;he&#x20;navigates&#x20;his&#x20;15th&#x20;year&#x20;leading&#x20;the&#x20;city.&#x20;Bell&#x20;delivered&#x20;the&#x20;State&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;City&#x20;address&#x20;last&#x20;Monday.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Durham Mayor Bill Bell is focused on improving transportation and reducing poverty as he navigates his 15th year leading the city. Bell delivered the State of the City address last Monday.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/sarah-kerman">Sarah Kerman</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">February 22, 2016 | 12:02am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
